trans-unit.source: Provides a standard set of component-related commands, which have predefined key input gestures and <xref:System.Windows.Input.RoutedUICommand.Text%2A?displayProperty=fullName> properties.
trans-unit.target: Ger en standarduppsättning med komponenten-relaterade kommandon som har fördefinierade nyckel inkommande gester och <xref:System.Windows.Input.RoutedUICommand.Text%2A?displayProperty=fullName> egenskaper.

trans-unit.source: The commands in the ComponentCommands class and commands in the other command library classes, such as <xref:System.Windows.Input.ApplicationCommands> and <xref:System.Windows.Input.NavigationCommands>, are intended to represent a set of common commands that application programmers encounter frequently.
trans-unit.target: Kommandon i klassen ComponentCommands och kommandona i det andra kommandot biblioteket klasser som <xref:System.Windows.Input.ApplicationCommands>och <xref:System.Windows.Input.NavigationCommands>, motsvarar en uppsättning kommandon som programmerare uppstår ofta.</xref:System.Windows.Input.NavigationCommands> </xref:System.Windows.Input.ApplicationCommands>

trans-unit.source: The commands only represent the instance of the <xref:System.Windows.Input.RoutedCommand> and not the implementation logic for the command.
trans-unit.target: Kommandona endast representerar instansen av den <xref:System.Windows.Input.RoutedCommand>och inte implementering logik för kommandot.</xref:System.Windows.Input.RoutedCommand>

trans-unit.source: The implementation logic is bound to the command via a <xref:System.Windows.UIElement.CommandBindings%2A>.
trans-unit.target: Implementering logiken som är bunden till kommandot via <xref:System.Windows.UIElement.CommandBindings%2A>.</xref:System.Windows.UIElement.CommandBindings%2A>

trans-unit.source: For example, if the <xref:System.Windows.Input.ComponentCommands.MoveLeft%2A> command is executed on a control (the command target), the logic that performs the <xref:System.Windows.Input.ComponentCommands.MoveLeft%2A> command may not be provided by the command target, so the application writer is responsible for writing the logic that determines how the command target handles the command.
trans-unit.target: Till exempel om den <xref:System.Windows.Input.ComponentCommands.MoveLeft%2A>kommando körs på en kontroll (kommando mål) logik som utför den <xref:System.Windows.Input.ComponentCommands.MoveLeft%2A>kommandot kan inte tillhandahållas som mål-kommandot, så programskrivaren ansvarar för att skriva den logik som bestämmer hur kommandot målet hanterar kommandot.</xref:System.Windows.Input.ComponentCommands.MoveLeft%2A> </xref:System.Windows.Input.ComponentCommands.MoveLeft%2A>

trans-unit.source: Many controls do provide implementation logic, though, for many of the commands in the command library.
trans-unit.target: Många kontroller tillhandahåller implementering logik, men för många kommandon i kommando-biblioteket.

trans-unit.source: For example, the <xref:System.Windows.Controls.TextBox> class provides logic for the <xref:System.Windows.Input.ApplicationCommands.Paste%2A> command, <xref:System.Windows.Input.ApplicationCommands.Cut%2A> command, <xref:System.Windows.Input.ApplicationCommands.Copy%2A> command, <xref:System.Windows.Input.ApplicationCommands.Undo%2A> command, and <xref:System.Windows.Input.ApplicationCommands.Redo%2A> command.
trans-unit.target: Till exempel den <xref:System.Windows.Controls.TextBox>klassen innehåller logik för att den <xref:System.Windows.Input.ApplicationCommands.Paste%2A>kommandot <xref:System.Windows.Input.ApplicationCommands.Cut%2A>kommandot <xref:System.Windows.Input.ApplicationCommands.Copy%2A>kommandot <xref:System.Windows.Input.ApplicationCommands.Undo%2A>kommando, och <xref:System.Windows.Input.ApplicationCommands.Redo%2A>kommandot.</xref:System.Windows.Input.ApplicationCommands.Redo%2A> </xref:System.Windows.Input.ApplicationCommands.Undo%2A> </xref:System.Windows.Input.ApplicationCommands.Copy%2A> </xref:System.Windows.Input.ApplicationCommands.Cut%2A> </xref:System.Windows.Input.ApplicationCommands.Paste%2A> </xref:System.Windows.Controls.TextBox>

trans-unit.source: See the class documentation for particular control classes for more information.
trans-unit.target: Klassen dokumentationen för viss kontroll klasser för mer information.

trans-unit.source: For more information on commands and commanding, see [Commanding Overview](~/add/includes/ajax-current-ext-md.md).
trans-unit.target: Mer information om kommandon och drar till sig finns [drar till sig översikt](~/add/includes/ajax-current-ext-md.md).
